","tid":791034,"uid":44725,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:00:13.000Z","msg":"香港真係唔適合俾人番工<br />\n女人仲好D,社交偏向同情女人<br />\n男人打工好慘的,錢又唔係多,野又要做足100%,又要抵得鬧,除非你係世界仔識埋堆<br />\n唔係既話俾我都唔想番工"},{"pid":"a8af234db831b3cfa04dd1da5b69fe96296935b9","tid":791034,"uid":44725,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"香港真係唔適合俾人番工<br />\n女人仲好D,社會偏向同情女人<br />\n男人打工好慘的,錢又唔係多,野又要做足100%,又要抵得鬧,除非你係世界仔識埋堆<br />\n唔係既話俾我都唔想番工"},{"pid":"2baaaf3897ff27da4193fca26dad0cc77ca7568a","tid":791034,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"我。28，已經停左2個月，中途去左半個月旅行。"},{"pid":"968d209799c567064e5ba0eea740855a034d0955","tid":791034,"uid":154421,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:12:03.000Z","msg":"點解一定要人番工？"},{"pid":"07bf9fd7ce999252b919e7b4f113f7d3e6eca8c7","tid":791034,"uid":60451,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"親戚有人冇做野兩年幾 表兄弟黎<br />\n我覺得主要係佢過唔到自己心理關口<br />\n<br />\n自己都做過年幾廢青<br />\n我覺得係對自己失去信心所以先會咁"},{"pid":"26fd661f7d74e3d8c7a9b60f81dc246ffb01e61d","tid":791034,"uid":7125,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"我個妹都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企有錢都算 又唔撚係有錢窮到仆街 三餐都係屋企食仲夠膽問屋企攞零用 真係屋企人正正常常已經要感恩"},{"pid":"447699eb88a4f85d049a3275e1ecb9daa24a246d","tid":791034,"uid":122155,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"俾著係十年前嘅我 我會好鄙視呢種人<br />\n不過衣家嘅我叫做有一定同理心<br />\n比較能夠明白佢地嘅處境<br />\n對好多所謂「隱蔽青年」嚟講<br />\n返工嘅話 好多時啲工種都唔係自己想做嘅野<br />\n打工嘅心態真係純粹為搵兩餐<br />\n咁嘅生活真係好令人卻步"},{"pid":"6bfd1a1364a56f313b29965b8886d86383f0b5f2","tid":791034,"uid":199074,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"你阿哥都係選擇過自己想過既生活姐<br />\n好多人既夢想其實好簡單 只係想第2朝起身唔洗返工做奴隸姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2b75b1e6dcb840508da6d78aecd77019c7409c","tid":791034,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"有冇工唔駛同人交流協調<br />\n<br />\n就嚟完約，全email做野，唔駛面對面講野不知幾好"},{"pid":"cfb15581f05d9754d8c91cc0b1c98f264222e02e","tid":791034,"uid":76098,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"有，不過個個係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b697d036c1323e6fb2897c519cfd93d911cc4a","tid":791034,"uid":71748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:38:26.000Z","msg":"隱閉緊唔知點搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d23bc6ea035107e33049ffe67f803fdc5ed355","tid":791034,"uid":33796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"講緊我？"},{"pid":"cb891dde11b9eff9d5e0ddd50572cd7dbf46da51","tid":791034,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6270c3d0a1fed470a80835db7583213a76177463","tid":791034,"uid":133136,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"968d209799c567064e5ba0eea740855a034d0955","tid":791034,"uid":154421,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:12:03.000Z","msg":"點解一定要人番工？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"自己有錢養得掂自己 唔返工絕對無問題<br />\n但廿幾歲唔做野等屋企養 唔叫垃圾叫咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c08019db6940a8fec66b4107a0cd0f1f13ad66f","tid":791034,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"冇播，因為失業果個係我囉。<br />\n不知幾爽"},{"pid":"4bcf1386b061cb92d59cfb0bfc841d56f64da1c6","tid":791034,"uid":27568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c08019db6940a8fec66b4107a0cd0f1f13ad66f","tid":791034,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"冇播，因為失業果個係我囉。<br />\n不知幾爽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:53:53.000Z","msg":"食窮人地緊係爽<br />\n除非大把錢"},{"pid":"b19442ccc361d671e0963b4d3070c6b8f328118f","tid":791034,"uid":197086,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"長期失業其實壓力都好大， 我建議搵啲part time做下先， 慢慢適應。"},{"pid":"d42ab1fb74975d092581e2279b3fd142e7576060","tid":791034,"uid":46933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:18:39.000Z","msg":"講個例子你聽<br />\n舅父三十幾失業(工廠工人only)<br />\n一失就失到60歲<br />\n一年最多做一個月散工買啤酒飲同寬頻錢<br />\n完全無錢<br />\n佢老母間租置屋落左佢名<br />\n所以綜援都攞唔到"},{"pid":"3bfcdfb7bb0eb734f1c1331e4df450cb5a142fd5","tid":791034,"uid":44725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b19442ccc361d671e0963b4d3070c6b8f328118f","tid":791034,"uid":197086,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"長期失業其實壓力都好大， 我建議搵啲part time做下先， 慢慢適應。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"壓力都係家人俾, 好多父母想仔女比家用, 都會逼佢地番工"},{"pid":"78d42bd5e88adb3ff6981b7a8937a86fb251557f","tid":791034,"uid":119102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c2b75b1e6dcb840508da6d78aecd77019c7409c","tid":791034,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"有冇工唔駛同人交流協調<br />\n<br />\n就嚟完約，全email做野，唔駛面對面講野不知幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:35:22.000Z","msg":"做倉庫"},{"pid":"26d78dd6fc073f5b6f85b9a9603da7f74fe6b15b","tid":791034,"uid":133038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"咁真係唔想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1e3d1a36597c51e66f7cd7e91e7ecedee50dc9","tid":791034,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"27歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im